本属包括以下物种：<ref>{{cite web |title=Arctoparmelia Hale |url=https://www.gbif.org/species/2605293 |website=GBIF}}</ref>
* [[离心北极衣|离心北极衣]] ''Arctoparmelia centrifuga'' (L.) Hale，离心北极梅
* ''Arctoparmelia centrifuga'' Linnaeus, 1753
* ''Arctoparmelia collatolica'' Chesnokov & Prokopiev
* [[曲北极衣|曲北极衣]] ''Arctoparmelia incurva'' (Pers.) Hale，曲北极梅
* [[平坦北极衣|平坦北极衣]] ''Arctoparmelia separata'' (Th.Fr.) Hale，平坦北极梅
* ''Arctoparmelia subcentrifuga'' (Oxner) Hale

